{"id":1198,"date":"2024-08-03T18:49:00","date_gmt":"2024-08-03T18:49:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1198"},"modified":"2024-08-03T18:49:00","modified_gmt":"2024-08-03T18:49:00","slug":"mission-012","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-012\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #012: Bad Babysitter"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Mission #012: Bad Babysitter<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Blizzard City, southeast house &#8211; woman in kitchen<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Completed main story missions up until Blizzard City<\/li>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm01-cut\/\">HM Cut<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Find a lost boy in a Pikachu costume on Route 8<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>TM27 Return<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>In Blizzard City there\u2019s a woman whose brother has gone missing on Route 8. If you track him down, she\u2019ll give you TM27 Return.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/012\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-southeast-house-in-blizzard-city.jpg\" alt=\"The southeast house in Blizzard City \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The southeast house in Blizzard City<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you enter Blizzard City from Route 8, head inside the first house you can see &#8211; it\u2019s the one on the southeast edge of it.<\/p>\n<p>Head upstairs into the apartment and you\u2019ll see a woman with a mission for you.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/012\/02-pokemon-unbound-her-brother-is-missing.jpg\" alt=\"Her brother is missing \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Her brother is missing<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The woman\u2019s brother is missing and you\u2019ll need to head back out onto Route 8 to find him.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/012\/03-pokemon-unbound-head-south-into-route-8.jpg\" alt=\"Head south into Route 8 \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Head south into Route 8<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Walk back out into Route 8 and head south. <\/p>\n<p>Don\u2019t continue east along the path &#8211; look for a small gap between a stand of trees and walk through it further south.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/012\/04-pokemon-unbound-through-the-gap.jpg\" alt=\"Through the gap \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Through the gap<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll find yourself on a ledge. <\/p>\n<p>Follow it around until you see a cliff you can jump off.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/012\/05-pokemon-unbound-jump-off-this-cliff.jpg\" alt=\"Jump off this cliff \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Jump off this cliff<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After you jump off, go east through the long grass on the ledge below.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/012\/06-pokemon-unbound-head-down-the-staircase.jpg\" alt=\"Head down the staircase \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Head down the staircase<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Walk down the steps south and you\u2019ll see a woman with blonde hair in the middle of a crossroads of sorts.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/012\/07-pokemon-unbound-the-crossroads.jpg\" alt=\"The crossroads \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The crossroads<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go past her, continuing south until you see a lower forested area blocked off by a couple of Cut trees.<\/p>\n<p>Cut them down, and you can get to the kid.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/012\/08-pokemon-unbound-the-kid-in-the-pikachu-costume-isnt-camouflaged-very-well.jpg\" alt=\"The kid in the Pikachu costume isn\u2019t camouflaged very well \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The kid in the Pikachu costume isn\u2019t camouflaged very well<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After you talk to him, he\u2019ll follow you all the way back to Blizzard City.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/012\/09-pokemon-unbound-the-sister-is-grateful.jpg\" alt=\"The sister is grateful \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The sister is grateful<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After you\u2019ve returned her brother, the woman gives you TM27 Return, which is kind of appropriate.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1199,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1198","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1198","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1199"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1198"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1198"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}